Package: EAVA
Type: Package
Title: Deterministic Verbal Autopsy Coding with "Expert Algorithm Verbal Autopsy"
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Emily Wilson, Henry Kalter, Abhi Datta, Sandipan Pramanik, Robert Black
